# Cloudflare Pages Configuration

## Build Configuration
Build command: npm run build
Build output directory: dist
Root directory: encrypther
Node version: 18

## Environment Variables (Optional)
# Add these in Cloudflare Pages dashboard if needed:
# PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
# PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-domain.com

## Notes
- Site automatically builds on every git push
- Preview deployments created for all pull requests
- Production deployment from main branch only
- Build time: ~5-8 seconds
- Output size: ~500KB gzipped

